com.google.api.services.fusiontables.model

Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<String,Object>
      • com.google.api.client.util.GenericData
        • com.google.api.client.json.GenericJson
          • com.google.api.services.fusiontables.model.Table
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Map<String,Object>

    public final class Table
extends GenericJson
    Represents a table. Specifies the name, whether it is exportable, description, attribution, and attribution link.

    This is the Java data model class that specifies how to parse/serialize into the JSON that is transmitted over HTTP when working with the Fusion Tables API. For a detailed explanation see: http://code.google.com/p/google-http-java-client/wiki/JSON

    Author:
    Google, Inc.
